OL,3,GOPINIONCWorth watching how new STV News
OL,4,Cservice plays out
OL,5,
OL,6,FIt was a dignified and understated
OL,7,Ffarewell to the STV News from Aberdeen.
OL,9,FOn Friday, presenter Norman Macleod
OL,10,Facknowledged the end of live
OL,11,Fbroadcasting from the city and said
OL,12,Fgoodbye to viewers.
OL,14,FThere was no coverage of the
OL,15,Fcontroversy surrounding the changes nor
OL,16,Fwas there any retrospective.
OL,18,FSTV is clearly hopeful the new look 6pm
OL,19,Fprogramme will be introduced as
OL,20,Fseamlessly as possible on Monday.
OL,23,EPub: 12-Jul-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
OL,24,ANext PageBClean FeedCNat TVFOn This Day
FL,146,140,200,120,0,100
PN,14502
SC,0002
CT,3,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F145A1784463086
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G2/7
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GOPINIONCWorth watching how new STV News
OL,4,Cservice plays out
OL,5,
OL,6,FActually it appears that the "new look"
OL,7,Fprogramme will look identical to the
OL,8,Fold service.
OL,10,FSTV had matching sets ` totally
OL,11,Fidentical as far as we can tell ` in
OL,12,Fboth Glasgow and Aberdeen. The branding
OL,13,Fwas identical.
OL,15,FOn Thursday viewers in the north saw a
OL,16,F6pm programme presented from Glasgow by
OL,17,Fthe Aberdeen-based presenter Andrea
OL,18,FBrymer.
OL,20,FYes, the real changes from Monday are
OL,21,Feditorial ` not cosmetic.
OL,23,EPub: 12-Jul-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
OL,24,ANext PageBClean FeedCNat TVFOn This Day
FL,146,140,200,120,0,100
