OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F145A1784463086
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G3/7
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GOPINIONCWorth watching how new STV News
OL,4,Cservice plays out
OL,5,
OL,6,FThe big question will concern the
OL,7,Fvolume and range of stories from the
OL,8,Fnorth ` both in the shared programme in
OL,9,Fboth areas and the northern sub-opt.
OL,11,FOfcom's new licence for STV North can
OL,12,Fbe read on the regulator's website.
OL,14,FOur reading of it is that it sets a
OL,15,Flimit on the amount of shared content
OL,16,Fin the 6pm programme ` there is not a
OL,17,Fminimum requirement as such for
OL,18,Fdedicated material from the north.
OL,20,FIn the long term this may prove
OL,21,Fsignificant.
OL,23,EPub: 12-Jul-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
OL,24,ANext PageBClean FeedCNat TVFOn This Day
FL,146,140,200,120,0,100
PN,14504
SC,0004
CT,3,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F145A1784463086
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G4/7
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GOPINIONCWorth watching how new STV News
OL,4,Cservice plays out
OL,5,
OL,6,FOn average over the week, there can be
OL,7,F1 hour 45 minutes of shared content at
OL,8,F6pm.
OL,10,FThat ` by implication ` leaves 45
OL,11,Fminutes a week left over.
OL,13,FThat 45 minutes would surely include
OL,14,Fthe 2 minute ad break at 6.28. So we're
OL,15,Fdown to a legal requirement which could
OL,16,Fbe met by just 7 minutes a night of
OL,17,FNorth content.
OL,23,EPub: 12-Jul-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
OL,24,ANext PageBClean FeedCNat TVFOn This Day
FL,146,140,200,120,0,100
PN,14505
SC,0005
CT,3,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F145A1784463086
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G5/7
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GOPINIONCWorth watching how new STV News
OL,4,Cservice plays out
OL,5,
OL,6,FThe licence would appear to allow the
OL,7,Foption of dropping more of the
OL,8,Fregionalised content whenever the
OL,9,Foverall duration is shorter ` say for
OL,10,Ffootball or a party political
OL,11,Fbroadcast.
OL,13,FAnd what will happen in the future if
OL,14,Fthe regular duration is cut? This would
OL,15,Fseem likely if C3 is ever allowed to
OL,16,Frun as many ads as non-PSB channels.
OL,18,FShould Ofcom have explicitly set a
OL,19,Fminimum requirement for the north?
OL,21,FAnyway the coming weeks could prove
OL,22,Finteresting.
OL,23,EPub: 12-Jul-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
OL,24,ANext PageBClean FeedCNat TVFOn This Day
FL,146,140,200,120,0,100
PN,14506
SC,0006
CT,3,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F145A1784463086
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G6/7
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GOPINIONCWorth watching how new STV News
OL,4,Cservice plays out
OL,5,
OL,6,FWhat is the balance between Scottish
OL,7,Fnational news and regional news?
OL,9,FHow hard will Ofcom work to provide a
OL,10,Fguarantee that the north is still
OL,11,Fgetting a service?
OL,13,FI really don't think STV are stupid or
OL,14,Fcynical enough to merely seek to comply
OL,15,Fwith the strict legal requirements of
OL,16,Fthe new licence.
OL,18,FThe company will surely want Northern
OL,19,Fviewers to feel reassured once they see
OL,20,Fthe new service. Whether they work is
OL,21,Fanother matter.
OL,23,EPub: 12-Jul-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
OL,24,ANext PageBClean FeedCNat TVFOn This Day
FL,146,140,200,120,0,100
PN,14507
SC,0007
