PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F145A1784463086
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G7/7
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GOPINIONCWorth watching how new STV News
OL,4,Cservice plays out
OL,5,
OL,6,FBut what if there are other changes by
OL,7,Fstealth further down the line?
OL,9,FFor now though, it must be accepted
OL,10,Fthat the changes are happening. Ofcom
OL,11,Fhas approved them.
OL,13,FThose of us who care about journalism
OL,14,Fshould wish the staff of STV well as
OL,15,Fthey cope with the changes. They
OL,16,Fopposed them but now have to make them
OL,17,Fwork.
OL,23,EPub: 12-Jul-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
